The,Avatar,API,allows,developers,to,get,a,user,s,profile,picture,and,real,name,based,on,their,email,address,This,can,be,used,to,personalize,email,based,communications,or,even,just,to,add,real,names,to,a,database,of,email,addresses,The,API,uses,public,profile,data,held,by,Google,which,includes,information,for,more,than,billion,users